snippet.textDisplay:
I too think that doubles serve no real purpose, with the pseudo-purposes being to show off ur balls and to save dirt and work.

Tables have less potential to harm u if u screw up and are much more solid than the shallow tips of a double's lip and landing. I wouldn't mind the extra work, if there is any extra work compared to doubles. I would argue that building 2 separate parts of the same jump is just as much, if not more work than building the same jump in 1 solid piece.
